node.text:
SHEIN X AUGUST IS OUT! 🔥
We're welcoming you back to design school with our latest edit! Find your faves from our new collection & share it with us for a chance to win some SHEIN gift codes!

Enter:
📚 Follow @sheinofficial & like this post
📚 Share your favorite look of the new collection
📚 Tag your besties!

Bonus: Share the post to your story with #SHEINX to double your chances of winning!

25 winners will be picked to get a $200 limited gift code to use specifically on our #SHEINX AUGUST collection on 8/26 via our stories!

Get a glimpse of the new collection NOW>> https://shein.top/55pg9zb

👉 Please Note:⁣

1. Your accounts need to be public so that we could see your entries.
2. The gift code needs to have an email address registered to a SHEIN account. Multiple winners with the same address would be treated as one winner with one gift code.
3. SHEIN reserves the right to final interpretation.

#SHEINX
